Welcome to Orlando!! Where the fake friends, hypocrisy, and drama are FREE... Yeah. Whatever. Right. I'm really tired of this place. *sighs* Just 2 years, 1 month, and 3 days...Then I'll be 18. But I have to wait to finish highschool. Then I SWEAR I'm getting the FU*K out of here. I don't give two shits where I go. If I have to live on the streets I will. As long as I'm out of Orlando. I don't care. Matt supposedly isn't EVER gonna let me live on the streets. Yeah. I'd like to see him stop me if thats what it comes to. Whatever. All this drama bullshit around here. All the fake people...Pretending to be shit they're not, the hypocrisy and contradiction of oneself...Saying they're true to themselves...But yet, have to be perfect for strangers and impress others. Right. Just GOTTA love it, right? Yeah. BULLSHIT. I don't think so. No thanksz, I'm ok. Leave me out of it. *sigh* Did I mention how Fu*king SICK and TIRED I am of all this CRAP?!?! Well...I am. Really. And I swear, the NEXT person that tells me to have "confidence" in "love" and shit cause I'm still young, I'm "only 16"...I'm gonna shoot their fu*king brains out. Don't tell me to be patient..Don't tell me that "things will get better with time" and all that crap. I'm tired. Yeah, I'm 16 ((or at least gonna be in like a month)), but what the fu*k ever. That doesn't mean that relationships aren't important to me. Cause they damn well are whether you like or not, whether they are to you or not. I don't give a shit cause I sure as hell aren't you. K? Thanksz! Right now, what I want, is a relationship...One thats fu*king truthful for ONCE...But I guess thats asking WAY too fu*king much of this forsaken world. Yeah, kiss my ass world...I hate you. *forced smile* Don't you hate those smiles? Those fake ones that you force upon yourself to hide your pain...And the funny thing is, people believe it. They truly believe you are one happy sunuvabitch, happy with your life...While inside you're screaming "You FU*KING idiot!! I am NOT happy, I WANT to die, I HATE you, See through my MASK dipshit!!" But you just don't feel like it...Yeah. You hate those smiles, yet you use them. Cause faking a smile is just soooo much easier then explaining why you're NOT smiling. Why you're NOT happy...Why you WANT to die. You DON'T want to have to explain your problems to another person. It makes you feel weak. Pathetic. Wounded. Left out in the open, exposed, for ANYONE to just come in and hurt you MORE. Like you need that bullshit. *sigh* Alright. Im pretty sure everyones wondering WTF is wrong with this crazy ass bitch. Alright, lets see, I was born, how bout that!! 

Anywho. Im crying right now. And Im kinda confused as to the reason. I dont know why I act like this and I wonder how I manage to always fu*k EVERYTHING up. Confused? Im sure. Just let me rant and well possibly get into an explanation of this all. Who knows. 

But yeah. Im at Crystals. Marks here too. I totally fu*king love her with EVERYTHING. Thats my ultimate best friend. I think she understands me the most out of everyone in this godforsaken world. We went to the mall. Played DDR ((duh)) and saw 2..count em, 2...Movies.."Fun with Dick and Jane" and "The Producers". They were pretty cool. I fell asleep during part of the Producers. I was bored, sitting by myself. Which was what I wanted...But...I dont know? Buuuut. Yeah. Theyre in the other room and Im ALMOST positive theyre passed out. I could be completely wrong and theyre doing the complete opposite...Again...HAHAHA. Love chu Crystal! Lol. But yeah. So, tomorrows New Years Eve and according to Crystal...We are getting completely fu*king wasted. Eh, fun...But not so much without a guy...Lol. Mark doesnt count...Not for me. Yeah. Whatever. A new year. Another year for me to completely fu*k up. *sigh* Oh yay...((note the sarcasm)) This year sucked. The new one is bound to be just as bad. Who knows, could be worse. Lord knows how THAT would be possible...*shrugs shoulders* I dont know, Ill manage something. *sigh* 

So..Ive given up on relationships. Im...nothing. I told Jason and he asked me what I was then. And I told him...Nothing, Just lonely for the rest of my fu*king life. But hey, Ive known that from the beginning...Now, Ive completely given up on looking for a relationship or boyfriend or whatever. Hell, I should just stop liking people cause NOONE fu*king likes me. Cant say Im surprised though. Ever since I was younger, boys didnt notice me. Not as a "girlfriend" thing. Just friends. God I hate being friends with guys that I know I want to be with. It totally sucks. Oh well...Whatever. And now I think Jason hates me...Fu*king great. Im just about the smartest fu*king person on this Earth. 

Where the hell is my pillow when I need it damnit. The one time I didnt carry it with me, I totally need it. Alyssa and Jaymme know what Im talking about. Ok...Let me explain my pillow to you other humans..I have this pillow. And when I sleep at night, I hold it...I dont let go of it. When I cry, I cry on it..I have a million tear stains on it. Alyssa and Jaymme have seen it. Millions. Whenever Im home, Its basically my ONLY comfort...If I ever lost that pillow. I would become a wreck. Whenever I feel down and shit...That pillow is with me the whole time. If I move to my corner ((yes I have a corner...its in my closet with writing all on the walls...anyways)) the pillow tags along...It doesnt leave my arms. The thing is, I dont wanna wash the tear stains off cause theyre memories...Theyre my past. Whenever I see them, they remind me of those things that made me cry...I dont know exactly how good that is..But, oh well. Nonetheless...Thats my pillow...Thats my comfort...And right about now, I need it...Badly..=(

I hate life...Life hates me...
Its a non-ending cycle. 

*sigh*

Why the fu*k am I still writing?
Im going to bed. Im damn tired. Im going to go cry myself asleep listening to Panic! At the Disco. <3333

And for all you scenesters and mainstream little fu*ks...If yall try to steal this band like youre <u>TRYING</u> to do to my band From First to Last...I will KILL you...Stop you fu*king preps, leave our music to us...Go listen to Gwen Stefani or some other dumb shit like that...

Your Lonely Princess and Fallen Angel,
XOXOXOXOXOX

The Corridor...
I stand in this corridor...The doors are all locked...Noone opens them to me... There are no windows to escape...No lights to see... Im lost...and sure Ill never be able to leave... I will forever be stuck in this corridor...locked out of these places...Never to explore... I dont dare move...Ill only get more lost...Ill only be more destined to a life of nothing... But then...I hear a voice...Its faint...But its there...I want to go towards it...But Im frightened... Im not sure if I should take this chance...Ive always been locked out of peoples lives...Why would someone open to me now? I risk my life...I go...I start to see a light...and the voice is becoming more clearer... They call to me...They know my name? They befriend me...and I trust them... Im no longer stuck in that corridor...That evil corridor of loneliness, anger, and frightened thoughts... Im part of something...I can feel...Life isnt always fair I know this...But for now...Its not bad... ANd Im not in the corridor...Im not alone anymore I hope to never be thrown out into that dark corridor again... Cause who knows if Ill survive it again?
